column1:
Currently, practical projects utilising artificial intelligence technologies are already being implemented in the healthcare sector in Ukraine, for example:
●    digital vision screening using artificial intelligence;
●    cloud-based AI solutions that detect lesions and pathologies in the human brain;
●    state-of-the-art AI systems for reading X-rays;
●    laboratory diagnostics and the use of portable X-ray machines with artificial intelligence;
●	AI-driven phage therapy technology – an approach that uses artificial intelligence to select viruses to combat antibiotic-resistant bacteria;
●    an AI-based tool that helps doctors quickly generate accurate medical reports, reduce paperwork, save time, etc.;
●          An AI assistant for doctors (in pilot mode), etc.

